# Marketing and SEO Best Practices

## Meta Tags

- **Meta description**: 150-160 characters; compelling, keyword-rich
- **Title tag**: Descriptive, unique per page; include primary keyword
- **Viewport**: Required for mobile responsiveness

## Open Graph and Twitter Cards

- Include Open Graph tags for all pages (title, description, image, url)
- Twitter Card metadata for social sharing
- Use `summary_large_image` for visual impact

## Structured Data (JSON-LD)

- Schema.org Person type for personal profiles
- ProfessionalService for consulting/contracting
- Include: name, jobTitle, description, url, image, sameAs (social links)

## Personal Brand Principles

- **Authenticity**: Reflect true self; share genuine journey
- **Consistency**: Align messaging across pages and platforms
- **Value proposition**: Clear, concise statement of expertise
- **Storytelling**: Ground in data and real-world insights

## Technical SEO

- Canonical URLs; robots meta (index, follow)
- robots.txt and sitemap.xml
- Descriptive alt text for images
